Package: topoDistance
Type: Package
Title: Calculating Topographic Paths and Distances
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Ian J . Wang
Maintainer: Ian J. Wang <ianwang@berkeley.edu>
Description: topoDistance provides functions for calculating topographic distances and identifying and plotting topographic paths. Topographic distances can be calculated along shortest topographic paths or topographic least cost paths. Functions can map topographic paths on colored or hillshade maps and plot topographic cross sections (elevation profiles) for the paths.
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0)
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: igraph, gdistance, plotly, raster, RColorBrewer, scales, sp
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
Suggests: knitr, rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
